De nada.

00:31:56.830 --> 00:31:57.640
Tú come primero.

00:31:58.000 --> 00:31:59.110
Voy a llamar

00:31:59.110 --> 00:31:59.790
a Chen Fangzhou.

00:32:00.680 --> 00:32:02.160
